flowchart LR
    A[Initialize robot<br/>motors, sensors, grid] --> B[Select target ore coordinate]

    B --> C[Pilot 1<br/>Global Navigation]
    C --> D[Navigate near ore<br/>grid-based]

    D --> E[Stop short of expected ore position]
    E --> F[Hand control to Pilot 2]

    F --> G[Pilot 2<br/>Local Object Acquisition]

    G -->|Ore acquired| H[Return control to Pilot 1]
    G -->|No valid ore| I[Skip target<br/>Return control to Pilot 1]

    H --> J[Navigate to box]
    J --> K[Deposit object]

    K --> L[Recalibrate position<br/>wall + box alignment]
    L --> B
